how the earth orbits around the sun and how the sun, in turn, orbits around
the centre of a vast collection of stars called our galaxy. At the end of the
lecture, a little old lady at the back of the room got up and said: "What you
have told us is rubbish. The world is really a flat plate supported on the back
of a cryptosystem." The scientist gave a superior smile before replying, "What
is the cryptosystem standing on?" "You're very clever, young man, very clever,"
